page.title: 01Finchingfield area,general.
page.content: The area that we are studying is the North west part of Essex, between Braintree and Saffron Walden.The places that we are working on are Finchingfield,Wethersfield and the Wethersfield Air Base. The population of Finchingfield is about 1600 and Wethersfield has a population of about 1100. The main industry of the area is arable agriculture. One of the highest points on our map that we are studying is the Wethersfield Air Base in the north. The lowest point is the valley of the River Pant in the south of our area. Finchingfield is situated in the west of the area,the Wethersfield Air Base is in the North east and Wethersfield village is in the South East.
